All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AIPlayer
The AIPlayer class represents an abstract artificial intelligence (AI) player in a card game.
Card
The Card class represents a card in a card game.
CardType
The CardType enum represents the possible types of cards in a card game.
Color
The Color enum represents the possible colors of cards in a card game.
ConsoleColors
The ConsoleColors class provides ANSI escape codes for coloring text in the console.
Deck
The Deck class represents a deck of cards used in a card game.
DumbComputerPlayer
The DumbComputerPlayer class represents a simple computer player in a card game.
Game
The Game class represents the main logic of a card game.
HumanPlayer
The HumanPlayer class represents a player controlled by a human in a card game.
